metadata.name: Druid Princess in the Forest of Dawleetoo
metadata.description:
When the sun began to set, the Druid Princess in the forest of Dawleetoo knew it was time to go home. She had been out all day, exploring the forest and meeting the animals who lived there. 

As she walked through the forest, she felt a sudden chill. It was as if someone was watching her. She looked around, but saw nothing. She quickened her pace, but the chill only got stronger. Suddenly, she heard a voice calling her name. 

She turned around, but there was no one there. She began to run, but the voice kept calling her...
